nodes.bodyText: Generated code change due to testserver swagger change Azure/autorest.testserver@5b9079f#diff-e5c08ffaff754dcb1ad397a927e62526

The change to the testserver swagger seems to be odd. This method is supposed to have no input param and the stringBody should be set to null internally inside this method as this method is intended to put a null string only.

Converted to Builder.
Added elementType, default as ClassType.String. (not sure about naming, will enumValueType better?)
